  "texts": [
    "The distance transformation provides the pixels known as certain of a region that belongs to a nucleus.",
    "With a weighted threshold of the maximum distance transformation value we received sure foreground regions of an identified nucleus indicated as a marker.",
    "A connected component analysis labels these regions with any positive integers to separate these from the background.",
    "Processing these markers with a marker-based watershed method allows to allocate the unclassified regions of the image belonging to nuclei regions or not.",
    "The resulting region property provides sure coordinates of spatial locations of nuclei."
  ],
